00:02:02.660 --> 00:02:07.860
So, just a little bit about me and my background.

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:10.779
I grew up in the Rocky Mountain West.

00:02:10.779 --> 00:02:16.179
So, this is the area of Colorado, Idaho, Oregon, Utah.

00:02:16.179 --> 00:02:18.940
